Name: HMpTy
Version: 0.2.2
Summary: Tools for working with Hierarchical Triangular Meshes (HTMs). Generate HTMIDs, crossmatch sky-coordinates via angular separation and more
Home-page: https://github.com/thespacedoctor/HMpTy
Author: David Young
Author-email: davidrobertyoung@gmail.com
